---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../components/SectionHeader.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="Catalina Torres — editor who codes. Mission, vision, and the way the work gets done.">
  <SectionHeader label="§2" title="About" />
  <article class="prose">
    <h3>Vision</h3>
    <p class="lede">
      Remove "I don't have time for that" from the working vocabulary.
    </p>

    <h3>Values</h3>
    <ul class="values">
      <li><strong>Clarity</strong> — If it isn't understood, it doesn't work.</li>
      <li><strong>Precision</strong> — Cutting what's extra is as important as adding what's missing.</li>
      <li><strong>Practicality</strong> — The best solution is the one that actually gets used.</li>
      <li><strong>Translation</strong> — Between technology and people there's always a gap. My job is to close it.</li>
      <li><strong>Rescue</strong> — No useful data, process, or idea should be lost for lack of order.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Mission</h3>
    <p>
      Make administrative work take up less room. I edit processes, automate the repetitive, and digitize what still lives on paper — so the important becomes more visible and the boring, shorter.
    </p>

    <h3>Value proposition</h3>
    <p>
      I don't sell software. I look at how you work, find what slows things down, what repeats, what gets lost — and redesign it. Sometimes the solution is an automation. Sometimes it's about changing the question.
    </p>

    <p>
      Editing is not a single skill: it's translation, patience, judgment, and the moderately honest use of euphemisms to make a writer arrive at what the editor wants <em>(needs)</em> while being completely convinced it was their idea.
    </p>

    <p>
      The editorial judgment I've built since 2012 is not separate from the code I write now. It's the reason the code works.
    </p>

    <p>
      I am fluent in English and Spanish. I live in Edmonton, Alberta. I am available for freelance consulting, short-term contracts, and full-time roles in operations automation or AI implementation.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>
  .prose p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .prose .lede {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
  }
  .prose h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin: var(--s-2) 0 var(--s-3);
  }
  .prose .values {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--s-8);
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .prose .values li {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-2);
  }
  .prose .values strong { font-weight: 700; }
</style>
